sequenceDiagram
    actor PL as Player
    participant GE as game_engine
    participant SR as ScoringRule::StreakBonus

    Note over PL,SR: streak starts at 0 for every player

    GE->>PL: question 1
    PL->>GE: submit_answer (correct)
    GE->>SR: score(ScoringContext{correct=true, streak=0}) → ScoringOutcome{points: 1000, streak_multiplier: 1.0}
    GE->>GE: player.correct_streak = 1
    GE-->>PL: answer_result {points: 1000, streak_multiplier: 1.0}

    GE->>PL: question 2
    PL->>GE: submit_answer (correct)
    GE->>SR: score(ScoringContext{correct=true, streak=1}) → ScoringOutcome{points: 1500, streak_multiplier: 1.5}
    GE->>GE: player.correct_streak = 2
    GE-->>PL: answer_result {points: 1500, streak_multiplier: 1.5}

    GE->>PL: question 3
    PL->>GE: submit_answer (incorrect)
    GE->>SR: score(ScoringContext{correct=false, streak=2}) → ScoringOutcome{points: 0, streak_multiplier: 1.0}
    GE->>GE: player.correct_streak = 0 (reset)
    GE-->>PL: answer_result {points: 0, streak_multiplier: 1.0}

    GE->>PL: question 4
    Note over GE: player does not answer before timer
    GE->>GE: do_end_question: player.correct_streak = 0 (timeout reset)
